VIRTUAL AVATAR ...try it virtually

  • A virtual fitting room is a type of technology that lets shoppers try on items virtually.
  • The augmented reality (AR) or artificial intelligence (AI) technology places the item over live imaging of the customer, so they can check the size, style, and fit of a product they’re thinking of buying
  • Most virtual fitting rooms work using augmented reality.
  • Virtual reality technology overlays the scanned products on the 3D model of the shopper.
